title: Episode 226: Lip Service Live Tour Houston (Feat. Carl Crawford, Slim Thug & Plies)
itunes:title: Episode 226: Lip Service Live Tour Houston (Feat. Carl Crawford, Slim Thug & Plies)
description:
Former Baseball player Carl Crawford, as well as Rappers Slim Thug and Plies, join the ladies of Lip Service during their live tour in Houston. Carl Crawford speaks on letting Evelyn Lozada keep her 1.4 million dollar engagement ring, Slim Thug opens up about why he got a vasectomy, Plies gives you the truth behind Sweet Pussy Saturday, and much more. Enjoy!
